The system should be easy to use for all types of users
The system should provide feedback to users when actions are performed
The data stored in the database should be as accurate as possible
Any battery power devices used should be energy efficient
The UI should work on a large variety of devices
The UI should run smoothly
The system should be secure
The system should be able to handle a large amount of users
The system should ignore any messages not part of the system
The UI should be accessible to all types of users including those with disabilities
The colour schemes used should be appropriate
The system should not collect more data than necessary
It should be easy for a user to connect parts of the system together
The system should respect users' privacy
